    "description": "Embark on an epic adventure in 'Slime Mutation,' a thrilling top-down arena shooter where you take on the role of a resilient slime facing relentless waves of creatures. Survive, evolve, and conquer in this rogue-like survivor indie game, crafted with love and dedication by a solo developer.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn 'Slime Mutation,' you'll experience heart-pounding action as you battle hordes of creatures. Collect valuable in-game currency to upgrade your slime's capabilities in a unique shop. Enhance your slime's skills and become an unstoppable force in this challenging world.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nUnleash your inner strategist and adapt to each wave of enemies as you evolve your slime into a formidable combatant, thanks to the various items you'll collect during your playthroughs. Understand their uses, but be cautious, as not all of them are worth taking. 'Slime Mutation' is a testament to the passion of indie game development and the creativity of a single developer.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAre you ready to mutate, survive, and thrive in the world of Slime Mutation? Join the adventure today and experience the thrill of evolution and conquest",
